From: Andre Klapper <a9016009@gmx.de>
Date: Sun, 12 Oct 2025 14:46:23 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 23/50] Backport some smaller fixes to external Seld/JsonLint

Summary:
Make PhpStan not complain anymore about:
* `/externals/jsonlint/src/Seld/JsonLint/JsonParser.php:121    Method JsonLintJsonParser::lint() should return JsonLintParsingException|null but return statement is missing.`
** https://github.com/Seldaek/jsonlint/commit/7e28add45b3a1c2392ca2a372adb9828ab0c7add
* `/externals/jsonlint/src/Seld/JsonLint/JsonParser.php:301    Method JsonLintJsonParser::performAction() invoked with 7 parameters, 6 required.`
** https://github.com/Seldaek/jsonlint/commit/811ee37714ae18a012cf05bd9dec3cd6baf4ae00
** https://github.com/Seldaek/jsonlint/commit/78a1ff3f47cd9cd79a14f1b352f3fb51794f6abc
* `/externals/jsonlint/src/Seld/JsonLint/JsonParser.php:324    Unreachable statement - code above always terminates.`
** https://github.com/Seldaek/jsonlint/commit/7e28add45b3a1c2392ca2a372adb9828ab0c7add
* `/externals/jsonlint/src/Seld/JsonLint/Lexer.php:189    Unreachable statement - code above always terminates.`
** https://github.com/Seldaek/jsonlint/commit/7e28add45b3a1c2392ca2a372adb9828ab0c7add

Test Plan: Run static code analysis.

Reviewers: O1 Blessed Committers, mainframe98

Reviewed By: O1 Blessed Committers, mainframe98

Subscribers: tobiaswiese, valerio.bozzolan, Matthew, Cigaryno

Differential Revision: https://we.phorge.it/D26415
---
 externals/jsonlint/src/Seld/JsonLint/JsonParser.php | 5 ++---
 externals/jsonlint/src/Seld/JsonLint/Lexer.php      | 2 --
 2 files changed, 2 insertions(+), 5 deletions(-)

diff --git a/externals/jsonlint/src/Seld/JsonLint/JsonParser.php b/externals/jsonlint/src/Seld/JsonLint/JsonParser.php
index ed3106ea5bfc..fe449e2ea901 100644
--- a/externals/jsonlint/src/Seld/JsonLint/JsonParser.php
+++ b/externals/jsonlint/src/Seld/JsonLint/JsonParser.php
@@ -123,6 +123,7 @@ class JsonLintJsonParser
         } catch (JsonLintParsingException $e) {
             return $e;
         }
+        return null;
     }
 
     /**
@@ -298,7 +299,7 @@ class JsonLintJsonParser
                         'first_column' => $this->lstack[count($this->lstack) - ($len ? $len : 1)]['first_column'],
                         'last_column' => $this->lstack[count($this->lstack) - 1]['last_column'],
                     );
-                    $r = $this->performAction($yyval, $yytext, $yyleng, $yylineno, $action[1], $this->vstack, $this->lstack);
+                    $r = $this->performAction($yyval, $yytext, $yyleng, $yylineno, $action[1], $this->vstack);
 
                     if (!$r instanceof JsonLintUndefined) {
                         return $r;
@@ -320,8 +321,6 @@ class JsonLintJsonParser
                     return true;
             }
         }
-
-        return true;
     }
 
     protected function parseError($str, $hash)
diff --git a/externals/jsonlint/src/Seld/JsonLint/Lexer.php b/externals/jsonlint/src/Seld/JsonLint/Lexer.php
index d002b5807b90..02c33c867d0b 100644
--- a/externals/jsonlint/src/Seld/JsonLint/Lexer.php
+++ b/externals/jsonlint/src/Seld/JsonLint/Lexer.php
@@ -186,10 +186,8 @@ class JsonLintLexer
             break;
         case 1:
             return 6;
-           break;
         case 2:
             $this->yytext = substr($this->yytext, 1, $this->yyleng-2);
-
             return 4;
         case 3:
             return 17;
